# config/package-lists/safety-filtering.list.chroot
# School-safe web filtering. PLAN.md "Safety" + AGENTS.md §13 defaults.
# Changes to safety-default packages auto-apply touches-safety-defaults
# label (per policies/sensitive-change-labels.yml).

dnsmasq                  # local DNS resolver for school-safe DNS rewrites
e2guardian               # optional content-filter proxy
ca-certificates
iptables
nftables
